name: Pura Luhur Mekori

review 1:
This place is huge, it has a big monkey population.

You must be respectful when going there. Please cover your shoulders and knees and pay respect to it.

There is a whole community that goes there to pray.
review 2: Temple with a small patch of forest. Did not manage to go in but the atmosphere there was nice, particulalry because of the big trees around the temple.
review 3: The one of temple in pupuan area. Have a mongkey forest also there. So just be careful with ur belonging when u go there
review 4:
One of interest temple which should be visit and pray during trip to Singaraja.
Be carefull with thw monkey
review 5: Pray for safety on the road.  There are alot of monkey on the temple
